{"tid":1631282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【最新】政府澄清有關「緊急法」謠傳","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:10:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:54:33.000Z","uid":51620,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d66b08e398d20e2aa3f20cffe2af67ecf10d08f1","tid":1631282,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:10:57.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】有關社交媒體傳言指行政長官即將再根據「緊急法」（即《緊急情況規例條例》）宣布星期二及三停市，停工及停學；並且凍結香港人的資產，政府發言人今日（十月六日）澄清有關傳聞純屬謠言，絕非事實。<br />\n<br />\n發言人稱，政府考慮到目前公共安全受到廣泛危害的迫切情況，訂立《禁止蒙面規例》，以加強警隊執法和對意圖違法者產生阻嚇作用，遏止暴力，盡快讓香港社會回復平靜。這絕非隨意的做法，而是一個困難但必須的決定。<br />\n<br />\n至於有關香港金融管理局（金管局）會訂立《提款法》限制市民每日提款金額的傳言，金管局今日已經發表聲明，強調絕無此事。該局並指香港銀行體系十分穩健，銀行有充足流動資金應付市民的需要。<br />\n<br />\n發言人提醒市民要認清這些社交媒體謠傳的意圖，是製造恐慌，令香港社會陷入進一步混亂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />777特區出嚟澄清嘅一定做"},{"pid":"e145ebc561b111cad919ef3c3b85182923c0954d","tid":1631282,"uid":267600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:22:12.000Z","msg":"已不再相信這個政府。"},{"pid":"fc0f4bacb302da071616c7601c4e06c950748236","tid":1631282,"uid":2267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:50:09.000Z","msg":"無認受性嘅政府，點解我要信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e9a9262f60bf1e893d0a686f2b63deb61a95b74","tid":1631282,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:52:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BwwPKTG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBwwPKTG.png&h=0da367c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30446a1c1473cd69c86304da2b0955d4afcf4db8","tid":1631282,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc0f4bacb302da071616c7601c4e06c950748236","tid":1631282,"uid":2267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:50:09.000Z","msg":"無認受性嘅政府，點解我要信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:52:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有10幾萬警察家屬認受特區政府"},{"pid":"b53cc158047789fd62e34f2dd6d6e2de6527ff82","tid":1631282,"uid":50194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:53:55.000Z","msg":"銀行有充足流動資金應付市民的需要???<br />\n兩日都無ATM有錢襟啊 屌你老母垃圾政府哪有錢?"},{"pid":"393cf1fd74e832702aad5f5c2799ebb0b9aae25f","tid":1631282,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:54:33.000Z","msg":"而家已經唔係信件事係咪真<br />\n而係唔信講呢件事既人/機關"}]}